    "description_quality": {
        "score": 85,
        "error_tags": ["MISSING_KEY_ENTITY"]
    },
    "assessment_quality": {
        "score": 70,
        "error_tags": ["VAGUE_REASONING"]
    },
    "recommendation_quality": {
        "score": 40,
        "error_tags": ["MISSING_CONTAINMENT", "GENERIC_ADVICE"]
    }
}
```

Based on this, it's clear the LLM is good at the high-level description and impact assessment, but it falls short on providing detailed reasoning and, most critically, lacks specific, action-oriented recommendations for immediate incident response.

